    "title": "Supply Chain Manager - Shadowfax - Freshers Welcome",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Shadowfax. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Supply Chain Manager to strengthen our Rajkot-based team.\n\nAbout Shadowfax:\nShadowfax is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure compliance with transportation regulations and safety standards\n• Implement warehouse management systems (WMS) and track KPIs\n• Manage reverse logistics and return merchandise authorization\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n• Conduct periodic vendor audits and evaluate logistics partners\n• Optimize delivery routes to reduce cost and improve efficiency\n• Implement cost-saving initiatives in transportation and warehousing\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in GPS Tracking Systems\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in Vendor Management\n• Proficiency in Route Optimization\n• Proficiency in Customs Clearance\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Learning & development budget\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Rajkot, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Shadowfax!",
